    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The actions, rites, ceremonies, or agreements surrounding a formal arrangement between a man and a woman to marry at some future time. An engagement or betrothal is a promise to wed, and also the period of time between a marriage proposal and a marriage which may be lengthy or trivial.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
